<!-- KLEIN DREAM INDEX - SUPER LOLITA EDITION -->
<style>
  :root{
    --kd-bg:#07152e;
    --kd-bg2:#0b2147;
    --kd-card:rgba(255,255,255,.075);
    --kd-card2:rgba(255,255,255,.045);
    --kd-line:rgba(255,255,255,.13);
    --kd-text:rgba(255,255,255,.94);
    --kd-muted:rgba(255,255,255,.74);
    --kd-faint:rgba(255,255,255,.56);
    --kd-accent:#7fc2ff;
    --kd-accent2:#b8e4ff;
    --kd-gold:#ffd36e;
    --kd-pink:#ffb6d7;
    --kd-green:#9cffbd;
    --kd-shadow:0 22px 70px rgba(0,0,0,.38);
  }

  *{box-sizing:border-box}

  .kd-index{
    min-height:100vh;
    color:var(--kd-text);
    font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,Arial,sans-serif;
    background:
      radial-gradient(900px 460px at 8% 8%, rgba(127,194,255,.22), transparent 58%),
      radial-gradient(700px 420px at 92% 8%, rgba(255,182,215,.16), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(900px 520px at 50% 110%, rgba(156,255,189,.10), transparent 62%),
      linear-gradient(180deg,var(--kd-bg),var(--kd-bg2) 55%,#061127);
    padding:26px 0 42px;
    overflow:hidden;
  }

  .kd-container{max-width:1150px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 18px;position:relative;z-index:2}

  .kd-stars:before,
  .kd-stars:after{
    content:"";
    position:absolute;
    inset:0;
    pointer-events:none;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,.45) 1px, transparent 1.5px),
      radial-gradient(circle, rgba(127,194,255,.40) 1px, transparent 1.5px);
    background-size:80px 80px,130px 130px;
    opacity:.28;
  }

  .kd-topbar{
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    align-items:center;
    gap:14px;
    margin-bottom:16px;
  }

  .kd-brand{
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    gap:10px;
    font-weight:950;
    letter-spacing:.2px;
    color:white;
    text-decoration:none;
  }

  .kd-brand-icon{
    width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:12px;
    display:grid;place-items:center;
    background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(127,194,255,.28),rgba(255,255,255,.08));
    border:1px solid var(--kd-line);
    box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.28);
  }

  .kd-nav{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;justify-content:flex-end}
  .kd-nav a{
    color:var(--kd-accent2);text-decoration:none;font-weight:800;font-size:13px;
    padding:8px 10px;border-radius:999px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);
    background:rgba(0,0,0,.14);
  }
  .kd-nav a:hover{background:rgba(127,194,255,.16);color:white}

  .kd-hero{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:1.08fr .92fr;
    gap:16px;
    align-items:stretch;
  }

  .kd-card{
    background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--kd-card),var(--kd-card2));
    border:1px solid var(--kd-line);
    border-radius:26px;
    box-shadow:var(--kd-shadow);
    backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
  }

  .kd-main-card{padding:24px;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
  .kd-main-card:after{
    content:"";position:absolute;right:-80px;top:-90px;width:240px;height:240px;border-radius:50%;
    background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(127,194,255,.20),transparent 62%);
  }

  .kd-kicker{
    display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;
    padding:8px 11px;border-radius:999px;
    border:1px solid rgba(127,194,255,.24);
    background:rgba(127,194,255,.12);
    color:var(--kd-accent2);
    font-size:12px;font-weight:900;
    margin-bottom:13px;
  }

  .kd-title{
    margin:0 0 12px;
    font-size:clamp(38px,6vw,66px);
    line-height:.96;
    letter-spacing:-2px;
    font-weight:1000;
  }
  .kd-title span{color:var(--kd-accent);text-shadow:0 0 24px rgba(127,194,255,.35)}

  .kd-lead{
    margin:0 0 16px;
    max-width:650px;
    color:var(--kd-muted);
    line-height:1.7;
    font-size:16px;
  }

  .kd-logo-box{
    margin:12px 0 16px;
    display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;
  }

  .kd-logo-box img{
    width:min(280px,100%);
    height:auto;
    border-radius:22px;
    border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);
    background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);
    box-shadow:0 16px 45px rgba(0,0,0,.32);
  }

  .kd-logo-note{
    flex:1;min-width:220px;
    padding:14px;border-radius:20px;
    background:rgba(0,0,0,.16);
    border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.10);
    color:var(--kd-muted);
    line-height:1.6;
    font-size:14px;
  }

  .kd-actions{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;margin:14px 0}
  .kd-btn{
    display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:8px;
    padding:12px 15px;border-radius:16px;
    color:white;text-decoration:none;font-weight:950;
    background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(127,194,255,.30),rgba(127,194,255,.16));
    border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.20);
    box-shadow:0 10px 28px rgba(0,0,0,.22);
    transition:transform .10s ease, filter .12s ease, background .12s ease;
  }
  .kd-btn:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);filter:brightness(1.08)}
  .kd-btn.secondary{background:rgba(0,0,0,.18);color:var(--kd-accent2)}
  .kd-btn.gold{background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,211,110,.28),rgba(255,211,110,.12));color:#fff7d8}
  .kd-btn.pink{background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,182,215,.28),rgba(255,182,215,.12));color:#ffeaf4}

  .kd-terms{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;color:var(--kd-faint);font-size:12px;margin-top:2px}
  .kd-terms a{color:var(--kd-accent2);text-decoration:none}.kd-terms a:hover{text-decoration:underline}

  .kd-badges{display:flex;gap:9px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:14px}
  .kd-badge{display:inline-flex;gap:8px;align-items:center;padding:8px 10px;border-radius:999px;background:rgba(0,0,0,.16);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.11);color:var(--kd-muted);font-size:12.5px;font-weight:750}
  .kd-dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:999px;background:var(--kd-accent);box-shadow:0 0 0 4px rgba(127,194,255,.16)}

  .kd-side{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px}
  .kd-side-card{padding:18px}
  .kd-side-card h2,.kd-section h3{margin:0 0 10px;font-weight:1000;letter-spacing:-.3px}
  .kd-side-card h2{font-size:19px}.kd-section h3{font-size:25px}
  .kd-side-card p,.kd-section-sub{margin:0;color:var(--kd-muted);line-height:1.65;font-size:14.5px}

  .kd-mini-list{list-style:none;margin:13px 0 0;padding:0;display:grid;gap:9px}
  .kd-mini-list li{padding:11px 12px;border-radius:17px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.11);background:rgba(0,0,0,.14);color:var(--kd-muted);line-height:1.45;font-size:13px}
  .kd-mini-list b{display:block;color:var(--kd-accent2);font-size:14px;margin-bottom:3px}

  .kd-showcase{
    margin-top:16px;
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
    gap:14px;
  }

  .kd-project{padding:18px;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
  .kd-project:before{content:"";position:absolute;right:-50px;top:-50px;width:150px;height:150px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(127,194,255,.13)}
  .kd-project.pet:before{background:rgba(255,211,110,.17)}
  .kd-project.paynt:before{background:rgba(255,182,215,.15)}

  .kd-project-head{display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:center;margin-bottom:10px;position:relative;z-index:1}
  .kd-project-icon{width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:16px;display:grid;place-items:center;font-size:25px;background:rgba(0,0,0,.18);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.13)}
  .kd-project h3{margin:0;font-size:21px;font-weight:1000}.kd-project small{color:var(--kd-faint);font-weight:800}
  .kd-project p{position:relative;z-index:1;color:var(--kd-muted);line-height:1.65;margin:0 0 13px;font-size:14.5px}

  .kd-pet-preview{
    position:relative;z-index:1;
    min-height:140px;
    border-radius:22px;
    border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);
    background:linear-gradient(#8fd1ff 0 48%,#8a5528 49% 100%);
    overflow:hidden;
    margin-bottom:12px;
  }
  .kd-pet-house{position:absolute;left:26px;bottom:18px;width:92px;height:66px;background:#b8592e;border:3px solid #6b2d15;border-radius:5px}
  .kd-pet-house:before{content:"";position:absolute;left:-12px;top:-32px;width:116px;height:40px;background:#7c1f1f;border:3px solid #4b1010;clip-path:polygon(50% 0,100% 100%,0 100%)}
  .kd-pet-dog{position:absolute;right:42px;bottom:22px;font-size:60px;animation:kdDog 1.2s infinite alternate ease-in-out;filter:drop-shadow(0 8px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.25))}
  .kd-pet-heart{position:absolute;right:35px;top:20px;font-size:26px;animation:kdHeart 1.5s infinite alternate ease-in-out}
  @keyframes kdDog{from{transform:translateY(0) rotate(-2deg)}to{transform:translateY(-8px) rotate(2deg)}}
  @keyframes kdHeart{from{opacity:.55;transform:translateY(0) scale(.95)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(-9px) scale(1.1)}}

  .kd-sections{margin-top:16px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:12px}
  .kd-feature{padding:16px;border-radius:22px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.11);background:rgba(0,0,0,.13)}
  .kd-feature h4{margin:0 0 7px;font-size:15px;color:var(--kd-accent2);font-weight:1000}
  .kd-feature p{margin:0;color:var(--kd-muted);line-height:1.55;font-size:13.5px}

  .kd-final{margin-top:16px;padding:20px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:14px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap}
  .kd-final h3{margin:0 0 6px;font-size:23px}.kd-final p{margin:0;color:var(--kd-muted);line-height:1.6;font-size:14.5px}

  @media(max-width:960px){
    .kd-hero,.kd-showcase{grid-template-columns:1fr}.kd-sections{grid-template-columns:1fr}.kd-topbar{align-items:flex-start;flex-direction:column}.kd-nav{justify-content:flex-start}.kd-main-card{padding:19px}.kd-title{letter-spacing:-1px}
  }
  @media(max-width:560px){
    .kd-index{padding-top:12px}.kd-container{padding:0 10px}.kd-card{border-radius:20px}.kd-actions .kd-btn{width:100%}.kd-logo-note{min-width:100%}.kd-nav a{font-size:12px;padding:7px 9px}.kd-pet-dog{right:28px}.kd-pet-house{left:18px}.kd-title{font-size:39px}
  }
</style>

<div class="kd-index kd-stars">
  <div class="kd-container">
    <div class="kd-topbar">
      <a class="kd-brand" href="/">
        <span class="kd-brand-icon">💾</span>
        <span>Klein Dream</span>
      </a>
      <nav class="kd-nav">
        <a href="/login">Entrar</a>
        <a href="/register">Criar conta</a>
        <a href="/termos">Termos</a>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <section class="kd-hero">
      <div class="kd-card kd-main-card">
        <div class="kd-kicker">✨ Internet antiga, coração novo</div>
        <h1 class="kd-title"><span>Klein</span><br>Dream</h1>
        <p class="kd-lead">
          Uma rede social com alma de internet antiga — mas com base moderna e estável.
          Aqui você não compete por atenção. Você constrói presença, história e conexão.
        </p>

        <div class="kd-logo-box">
          <img src="/img/logo1.png" alt="Logo Klein Dream">
          <div class="kd-logo-note">
            Perfil, fotos, recados, comunidades e pequenos projetos feitos com carinho.
            Uma vitrine nostálgica para quem sente falta de uma internet mais humana.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="kd-actions">
          <a class="kd-btn" href="/register">🌟 Criar minha conta</a>
          <a class="kd-btn secondary" href="/login">🔐 Entrar</a>
          <a class="kd-btn gold" href="https://kleindream.com.br/auau">🐶 Jogar Klein Dream Pet</a>
          <a class="kd-btn pink" href="https://klein-dream-paynt.onrender.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">🎨 Abrir Paynt</a>
        </div>
        <label class="kd-terms"><input type="checkbox" checked disabled> Ao entrar, você conhece e aceita os <a href="/termos">termos de uso</a>.</label>

        <div class="kd-badges">
          <div class="kd-badge"><span class="kd-dot"></span> Sem algoritmo sufocando</div>
          <div class="kd-badge"><span class="kd-dot"></span> Perfil completo e humano</div>
          <div class="kd-badge"><span class="kd-dot"></span> Nostalgia com estrutura real</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="kd-side">
        <div class="kd-card kd-side-card">
          <h2>O que você pode fazer agora</h2>
          <p>Uma rede simples, direta e feita para pessoas, não para barulho.</p>
          <ul class="kd-mini-list">
            <li><b>Perfil com foto</b> Mostre quem você é sem depender de feed infinito.</li>
            <li><b>Até 6 fotos no álbum</b> Guarde lembranças no estilo clássico da internet.</li>
            <li><b>Recados e depoimentos</b> Mensagens públicas e depoimentos com aprovação.</li>
            <li><b>Amizades e comunidades</b> Tópicos, conversas e gente real.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="kd-card kd-side-card">
          <h2>Por que isso importa?</h2>
          <p>
            Porque a internet virou barulho. A Klein Dream é um retorno à calma:
            menos disputa, mais conversa, mais perfil, mais identidade.
          </p>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </section>

    <section class="kd-showcase">
      <div class="kd-card kd-project pet">
        <div class="kd-project-head">
          <div class="kd-project-icon">🐶</div>
          <div>
            <h3>Klein Dream Pet — Auau</h3>
            <small>Um bichinho virtual feliz, simples e sem anúncios</small>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="kd-pet-preview" aria-label="Prévia do Klein Dream Pet Auau">
          <div class="kd-pet-house"></div>
          <div class="kd-pet-heart">💙</div>
          <div class="kd-pet-dog">🐶</div>
        </div>
        <p>
          Cuide do Auau: dê comida, carinho, banho, abrace, brinque e aproveite um joguinho leve
          para crianças, idosos e todos que querem um momento tranquilo no celular.
        </p>
        <a class="kd-btn gold" href="https://kleindream.com.br/auau">Jogar agora 🐾</a>
      </div>

      <div class="kd-card kd-project paynt">
        <div class="kd-project-head">
          <div class="kd-project-icon">🎨</div>
          <div>
            <h3>Klein Dream Paynt</h3>
            <small>Desenho nostálgico direto no navegador</small>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p>
          Uma experiência simples, leve e divertida para desenhar e editar imagens sem complicação.
          Uma amostra da qualidade e do carinho por trás do universo Klein Dream.
        </p>
        <a class="kd-btn pink" href="https://klein-dream-paynt.onrender.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Criar e editar imagens 🎨</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="kd-sections">
      <div class="kd-feature">
        <h4>💬 Recados de verdade</h4>
        <p>Aquela sensação gostosa de deixar uma mensagem no perfil de alguém, sem pressa e sem algoritmo.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="kd-feature">
        <h4>🏡 Comunidades</h4>
        <p>Um espaço para assuntos, lembranças, ideias e grupos com cara de internet clássica.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="kd-feature">
        <h4>🧡 Presença humana</h4>
        <p>Mais identidade, mais perfil, mais história. Menos barulho automático e menos competição por atenção.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="kd-card kd-final">
      <div>
        <h3>Entre sem pressa. Fique pelo sentimento.</h3>
        <p>A Klein Dream é pequena, mas tem alma. Cada novo membro ajuda esse sonho a continuar crescendo.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="kd-actions" style="margin:0">
        <a class="kd-btn" href="/register">Criar conta</a>
        <a class="kd-btn secondary" href="/login">Já sou membro</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</div>
